messages.message: Hi Team - anyone have any guidance on how to see commercial users usage? It seems like the usage is not showing up - there is a 12/20 run in Grafana that is the last run.... however I know they have used it more recently than that

This may be unrelated, but I see in this query that SGB has used 21 credits (https://aihub.instabase.com/grafana/explore?orgId=1&left=%7B%22datasource%22:%22mysql%22,%22queries%22:%5B%7B%22refId%22:%22A%22,%22datasource%22:%7B%22type%22:%22mysql%22,%22uid%22:%22mysql%22%7D,%22format%22:%22table%22,%22rawSql%22:%22SELECT%5Cr%5Cn%20%20accounts.public_id%20AS%20org_name,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20organization_profiles.full_name%20AS%20org_full_name,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20organization_profiles.organization_id%20AS%20org_id,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20IF%28valid_from,%20DATE_FORMAT%28FROM_UNIXTIME%28valid_from%29,%20%27%25Y-%25m-%25d%27%29,%20%27%27%29%20AS%20start_date,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20IF%28valid_until,%20DATE_FORMAT%28FROM_UNIXTIME%28valid_until%29,%20%27%25Y-%25m-%25d%27%29,%20%27%27%29%20AS%20end_date,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20IF%28%5Cr%5Cn%20%20%20%20FROM_UNIXTIME%28valid_until%29%20%3C%20CURRENT_TIME,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20%20%20%27YES%27,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20%20%20%27%27%5Cr%5Cn%20%20%29%20AS%20license_expired,%5Cr%5Cn%20%20COALESCE%28SUM%28resource_cost%20%2A%20usage_count%29,%200%29%20%2F%201e7%20as%20usage_in_consumption_units%5Cr%5CnFROM%5Cr%5Cn%20%20organizations%5Cr%5Cn%20%20LEFT%20JOIN%20organization_profiles%20ON%20organizations.id%20%3D%20organization_profiles.organization_id%5Cr%5Cn%20%20LEFT%20JOIN%20license_metrics%20ON%20organizations.id%20%3D%20license_metrics.organization_id%5Cr%5Cn%20%20LEFT%20JOIN%20license_assignment%20ON%20organizations.account_id%20%3D%20license_assignment.user_account_id%5Cr%5Cn%20%20LEFT%20JOIN%20accounts%20on%20organizations.account_id%20%3D%20accounts.id%5Cr%5Cn%20%20LEFT%20JOIN%20license_products%20ON%20license_products.id%20%3D%20license_metrics.product_resource_id%5Cr%5Cn%20%20LEFT%20JOIN%20licenses%20on%20license_assignment.ib_license_id%20%3D%20licenses.ib_license_id%5Cr%5CnWHERE%5Cr%5Cn%20%20license_products.id%20IS%20NULL%20OR%20license_products.resource_name%20%3D%20%27AIHUB_CONSUMPTION_UNITS%27%5Cr%5CnGROUP%20BY%5Cr%5Cn%20%201,%5Cr%5Cn%20%202,%5Cr%5Cn%20%203,%5Cr%5Cn%20%204,%5Cr%5Cn%20%205%5Cr%5CnORDER%20BY%5Cr%5Cn%20%201%5Cr%5CnLIMIT%5Cr%5Cn%20%20100%22,
